metadata.description: Tony Stewartâ€™s success on the track carried over as a successful owner of race teams, tracks, and even series. In 2020, Stewart co-founded a new All-Star racing series SRX (Superstar Racing Experience). Stewart won the inaugural SRX championship in 2021 at the finale event at the Nashville Fairgrounds Speedway in Nashville, TN. In 2022, returned to track to defend his crown and finished fourth overall.
